      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      rf-bfr-alf-mag       to   w-des-scr-002-cod      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Continuazione                           *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           go to     cpz-des-rgs-700.
       cpz-des-rgs-460.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se personalizzazione tipo : 03              *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
