      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "["                  to   w-des-scr-004-pqs      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Tipo codice                             *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-buf-rig-bfo-wtp    to   w-des-scr-004-tco      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Parentesi quadra destra                 *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "]"                  to   w-des-scr-004-pqd      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Codice                                  *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      rf-bfr-alf-mag       to   w-des-scr-004-cod      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Descrizione di 21 caratteri             *
