           move      rf-dcc-cat-scr       to   w-tes-csr-aac (1)      .
           move      rf-dcc-per-scr (1)   to   w-tes-psr-aac (1, 1)   .
           move      rf-dcc-per-scr (2)   to   w-tes-psr-aac (1, 2)   .
           move      rf-dcc-per-scr (3)   to   w-tes-psr-aac (1, 3)   .
