      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      w-acc                to   w-sav-val-acc          .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Bufferizzazione valori estratti                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      w-fnd-arc-bft-prt    to   w-acc-num-prt          .
